dataList.content: ... Nice hat you've got there. Where'd ya get it?

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: EEEK!! I-I’m sorry! Please, take everything! Take as much time as you want! H-here’s my watch!
Heathcliff was looming over the man and growling threateningly... He certainly fit the look of a ‘villain’ from this particular angle.
Lass, I was just complimenting him for his sharp fashion choices! The lad’s overreacting!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: T-this is literally everything I have…! I don’t got any money for ransom even if you were to kidnap me!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: P-please, please don’t kidnap me! I’ve got family… they're all waiting for me to come home…!!!
The man we inadvertently saved from the hands of thieves was shuddering and screaming incoherently, almost to an unnatural degree.
… And we were still not out of the dark alleyways where other thieves might be waiting to get the jump on us...

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: The hell is this racket… Oh?

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Well, well, well. What do we have ‘ere? I think I'm seein' loads of time rolling in right before us!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: Ten minutes! No, we’ll take five minutes, too! Hand it over, now!
Why the hell is every fella here so obsessed with time?!

dataList.title: T Corp.
dataList.content: If you won’t give it up willingly, we’ll have to kill you all and take that clock for ourselves!
